<h2 id="how-to-smoke-beef-short-ribs-step-by-step"   class="wp-block-heading" >How to Smoke Beef Short Ribs Step-by-Step</h2>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li><em>Optional: </em>The night before, season your ribs generously with salt. Let them rest in the fridge overnight, uncovered.</li>



<li>Preheat the smoker to 285°F and prepare a spray bottle with apple cider vinegar. Mix your remaining seasonings, then thoroughly season the meat on all sides, patting it down firmly. <br><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182104" style="width: 1200px;" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182104" style="width: 1200px;" src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-3-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></li>



<li>Smoke the ribs for 4 hours, spritzing it every hour with apple cider vinegar to keep them moist. You'll know it's done when a <a href="https://amzn.to/3IsWXe0" data-eafl-id="143011" data-eafl-text="meat thermometer" class="eafl-link button, shared-counts-button, social-facebook, social-instagram, social-pinterest, social-twitter, wp-block-social-link-anchor wpel-icon-right" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">meat thermometer<span class="wpel-icon wpel-image wpel-icon-6"></span></a> pierces the meat without any resistance! <br><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182103" style="width: 1200px;" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182103" style="width: 1200px;" src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-2-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></li>



<li>Remove the ribs from the smoker, serve, and enjoy!<br><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182102" style="width: 1200px;" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-150x225.jpg 150w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" class="wp-image-182102" style="width: 1200px;" src="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1.jpg" alt="" srcset="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1.jpg 1200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-360x540.jpg 360w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-180x270.jpg 180w, https://sundaysuppermovement.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/smoked-short-ribs-process-1-150x225.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></li>
</ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-group-lightbulb"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 id="isabels-top-tips-for-smoking-beef-short-ribs"   class="wp-block-heading" >Isabel's Top Tips for Smoking Beef Short Ribs</h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Any type of pellet will work</strong> for this smoked beef short rib recipe, but I always love hickory, cherry, or oak for beef.</li>



<li>If you're using particularly heavy ribs, check the beef at 4 hours and see if it needs longer. <strong>The meat should be butter soft and the internal temperature should read 190°F or higher</strong>. </li>



<li>I highly suggest <strong>using a pellet smoker</strong> for all smoked recipes. They're easy, versatile, and user-friendly. I have a <a href="https://amzn.to/3LytgMP" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow external" data-wpel-link="external" class="button, shared-counts-button, social-facebook, social-instagram, social-pinterest, social-twitter, wp-block-social-link-anchor wpel-icon-right">Wood Pellet Grill and Smoker<span class="wpel-icon wpel-image wpel-icon-6"></span></a> like this.</li>



<li>You don’t need a specific amount of apple cider vinegar; just give the meat a few spritzes to ensure it stays nice and moist!</li>



<li>For the perfect barbecue sauce, try my <a href="https://sundaysuppermovement.com/bbq-sauce/" data-wpel-link="internal" target="_blank">Sweet BBQ Sauce Recipe</a>.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<h2 id="faq"   class="wp-block-heading" >FAQ</h2>



<div class="schema-faq wp-block-yoast-faq-block"><div class="schema-faq-section" id="faq-question-1699295578930"><strong class="schema-faq-question">Do you wrap beef ribs when smoking?</strong> <p class="schema-faq-answer">Some recipes will wrap the ribs in peach butcher paper or aluminum foil for the last bit of smoking, but in my experience, you don't need to wrap beef ribs. I recommend not wrapping them and instead spritzing them every hour to keep the meat moist.</p> </div> </div>



